<HEADLINE> Tehran Stock Exchange Index Up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, March 1 (Xinhua) -- The general price index at Tehran
Stock Exchange on Monday closed at 1,526.19 points, up 2.23 points
from Sunday's finish.
</P>
