of the votes cast," the statement said.
</P>
<P>
General Obassanjo, a former military ruler who campaigned as
the only man capable of holding together this vibrant and
fractious country, on Sunday scored an overwhelming victory to
become the first elected president in the West African country in
16 years, initial election outcome said.
