<P>
He dismissed as false press reports in Monday's Monitor
newspaper that the WB has suspended the Bujagali project.
</P>
<P>
Both the WB and the IFC would work with the government and the
developer to resolve any other matters relating to the Bujagali
project, he added.  
</P>
</TEXT>
