total 3,014 proposals since the formation of the Ninth CPPCC
National Committee in March 1998, of which 2,664 have been
formally accepted for investigations. By February 10, nearly 2,
600 of them had been handled and their results reported to
proposal makers, accounting for 96.7 percent of the total,
according to Tian. 
