approaching and Macao will return to the embrace of motherland,
which provides Macao compatriots an opportunity to go hand in hand
with people of inland areas to realize new achievements."
</P>
<P>
The China Millennium Altar will be a symbol to carry forward
China's 5,000-year-old civilization and fine traditions and the
spirit of unity, independence and peace. It will serve as a window
for people of other countries to understand the splendid arts and
culture of China, he said.
</P>
<P>
Construction of the altar is now underway in Beijing, and a
special fund has been established to receive donations from
everyone.  
