<HEADLINE> Rafter, Ivanisevic Win Openers in Scottsdale Tennis </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, March 1 (Xinhua) -- Patrick Rafter of Australia and
Goran Ivanisevic of Croatia won their opening matches respectively
at the Franklin Templeton Tennis Classic in Scottsdale, Arizona on
Monday.
</P>
<P>
