<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, March 2 (Xinhua) -- The China Petroleum Materials and
Equipment (Group) Corp. (CPMEC) plans to acquire 400 million US
dollars in import and export contracts for 1999, with export
projected at 200-300 million dollars.
</P>
<P>
CPMEC, a venture established in 1992, is expected to earn 3.64
billion yuan in sales revenues and 26.46 million yuan in post-tax
profits.
</P>
