completing comprehensive materials purchasing for the refinery in
Sudan.
</P>
<P>
CPMEC also plans to further develop markets in South America,
the Middle East and North Africa and will at the same time
establish stable integrated export networks in related regions.
</P>
<P>
Last year, CPMEC put 490-million-dollar contracts into
operation and reached a trade balance of 174 million dollars, both
record high for the company, according to Zheng. Its contractual
export volume reached 260 million US dollars and profit earnings
hit 24.5 million yuan in the past year. 
