phone lines in a single family, according to the regulation.
</P>
<P>
This is part of a Ministry of Information Industry plan to cut
telephone installation fees as of March 1.
</P>
<P>
Many people joined a long line Monday morning in front of the
Beijing Municipal Telephone Office to apply for telephone
installation, eyewitnesses said.
</P>
<P>
There are now an average of 48 telephones for every 100
residents in the Chinese capital.  
